extends layout

block jumbotron
  header.jumbotron
    div.container
      h1 Mozilla One-and-Done
      p The "One and Done" initiative, previously known as "QA Taskboard", is a workflow where Mozilla community contributors can pick tasks and work on them - one at a time, one day at a time - and feel good about doing them.


block content
  p.lead Mozilla QA sees the "One and Done" initiative as a way for Mozilla community contributors to get introduced to various projects and then to become involved in an area of their interest.

  p Contributors would be able to find their voice in the community, be able to engage meaningfully, and feel rewarded for their contribution.
